This is an independent list of the best SEO companies in the UK, ranked by methodology, published results, and specialisation, not paid placements. As an independent SEO consultant based in London and Reading, Berkshire, I have no financial relationship with any agency listed here. I am included on this list myself (transparently labelled), which means you can evaluate my approach alongside theirs and decide which fits your business.

Most "best SEO agency" lists charge £500-£5,000 for a featured spot, so the companies on those lists paid to be there. This one does not work that way.

**Selection criteria:** verifiable case studies, publicly demonstrated methodology, client retention evidence, specialist depth or breadth of capability, and fit across different business types and budgets.

