## Best AI SEO and AEO Agencies UK

AI search optimisation (AEO, Answer Engine Optimisation) is the fastest-growing specialism in UK SEO. As ChatGPT, Perplexity, Bing Copilot, and Google AI Overviews reshape how users discover businesses, the agencies and consultants who can demonstrate real AI-search results will separate from those who simply added "AI" to their services page.

**What to look for in an AI SEO / AEO specialist:**
- Documented AI-search lead conversions (not just "we optimise for AI")
- Understanding of entity-based SEO (how LLMs parse and cite sources)
- Experience with structured data that AI crawlers extract
- Published methodology, not just marketing claims

Currently, very few UK SEO providers can demonstrate genuine AEO results. **Sunny Patel SEO** is the only consultant on this list with a verified AI-search lead conversion: a London healthcare client discovered through Bing Copilot citation. Read the full [AI search optimisation](/services/ai-search-optimisation/) methodology.

For businesses preparing for AI-powered search, also read: [how to optimise content for AI search](/blog/optimise-content-for-ai-search/) and [AI search statistics UK](/blog/ai-search-statistics/).

